      "description": "Looking for a reliable daily driver that won't break the bank? This vehicle is in fair condition and ready for its next adventure! It shows some honest wear from its time on the road, but it remains a solid, functional choice for anyone seeking dependable transportation at a great value. It\u2019s a hardworking car with plenty of character and many more miles to give!",
