      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair, functional condition and serves as a dependable option for anyone needing a solid daily driver. While the engine and transmission perform reliably, the exterior shows some noticeable clear coat peeling and minor dings consistent with its age. The interior is clean but exhibits typical wear on the upholstery and some fading on the dashboard plastics. It has been regularly serviced, though it may require some minor cosmetic attention or suspension work in the near future to bring it back to peak comfort.",
