    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, preserved in pristine condition. This unit represents the pinnacle of its class, featuring a flawless exterior and a meticulously maintained interior that reflects a standard of care rarely encountered in the pre-owned market. For the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing short of perfection, this offering stands as a definitive benchmark in automotive excellence and mechanical integrity.",
      "price": 48500.0,
