      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled distinction. This vehicle remains in impeccable showroom condition, exhibiting an exterior finish devoid of imperfections and an interior that retains its original factory integrity. Meticulously maintained and stored in a climate-controlled environment, its mechanical performance is flawless, reflecting a rigorous adherence to preventative maintenance protocols. This is a rare opportunity for the discerning collector to acquire a motorcar that represents the absolute zenith of its production class.",
      "price": 48500.0,
